I"(<h2 id="client">Client</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Generate SSH key pair
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ssh-keygen <span class="nt">-t</span> rsa
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Store public key on remote server
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ssh-copy-id <span class="nt">-i</span> ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub &lt;<span class="nv">$USER</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>@&lt;<span class="nv">$SERVER</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

<h2 id="server">Server</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/ssh/sshd_config</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>PasswordAuthentication no
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Restart SSH Service
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>service ssh restart
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

